title: Sex bolts
description: Sex bolts, also known as Chicago bolts, resemble machine screws, but with internal threads.

title: Mating screws
description: Mating screws have an unthreaded shoulder that is the same diameter as the outside of the sex bolts they are used with.

title: Chrome bolt covers
description: Decorative chrome covers for the heads of bolts and screws.

title: Double loop hitch pin clips
description: Double loop hitch pin clips are R-shaped clips with a coil to provide additional durability in clevis pin or hitch pin systems. Also known as bridge pins.

title: Rivet Nuts
description: Rivet nuts are useful for adding a load-bearing machine thread to sheet material applications and other thin surfaces. Available in a variety of types and sizes.

title: Flange nuts, prevailing torque
description: An all metal lock nut with a built in washer often used in high temperature applications. This style of lock nut deforms the threads of the mated fastener. Can be domed or flat style.
